---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Universal Tool — Wenji Makes" description="A deliberately overpowered all-in-one Stardew Valley tool and weapon.">
  <div class="mod-header"><div class="container">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px;"><span class="tag">Weapon</span><span class="tag">Tool</span><span class="tag">Power fantasy</span></div>
    <h1>Universal Tool — Extraterrestrial Meteor Ruler</h1><p class="meta">1.0.0 · SMAPI 4.0+ · Mod ID: 48087</p>
  </div></div>
  <section class="mod-content container">
    <img src="https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/1303/images/headers/48087_1782230075.jpg" alt="Universal Tool" class="mod-image-full" />
    <p><strong>An all-in-one tool forged from an extraterrestrial meteor: chop, mine, harvest, fight, permanently defeat mummies, and summon rotating swords.</strong></p>
    <p>This mod is deliberately built around power and spectacle. It also includes the “Weather Child” ability, which changes the weather and the environment around you.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul style="color:var(--text-muted);margin:12px 0 24px 20px;">
      <li>One tool for trees, rocks, crops, and combat</li><li>Finish mummies directly</li><li>Summon a rotating sword formation for area damage</li><li>Weather-changing ability</li><li>Unlocked through a specific in-game path</li>
    </ul>
    <div style="margin-top:40px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;"><a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/48087" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Download on Nexus Mods</a><a href="/en/mods" class="btn btn-outline">← Back to Mods</a></div>
  </section>
</Layout>
